##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       4834 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  4834 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   4834 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  4834 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  4834 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 4834 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   4834 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    4834 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    4834 1451
total cross section.                                              4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           4834 1451
                                                                  4834 1451
MT5 contains the reactions which can not be stored in any other   4834 1451
MT-number. The information of MF3/MT5 can be combined with        4834 1451
MF6/MT5 to obtain residual production cross sections particle     4834 1451
production cross sections and (double-)differential cross         4834 1451
sections.                                                         4834 1451
